-- Female Buyer Bids for Twickenham Film Studios, Telegraph Says
-- B y   A n n e - S y l v a i n e   C h a s s a n y
-- 2012-04-29T09:31:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-29/female-buyer-bids-for-twickenham-film-studios-telegraph-says.html
An unidentified female buyer
offered 100,000 pounds ($163,000) for Twickenham Film Studios
Ltd., the Sunday Telegraph said, without citing anyone.  Harry Potter author  J.K. Rowling  has expressed an in
interest in the future of the studios after one of the sequels
was filmed there, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
